location.fullValue: Dailey Plan, Edge at Downtown Superior

data.description: Gorgeous, completely remodeled home in Louisville! A newly constructed front porch welcomes you. Step inside the new front door to refinished solid hardwood floors, new non-VOC wool carpet, all new paint, modern door hardware, and gorgeous light fixtures throughout. 3 Bds up, including primary bdrm w/ luxury ensuite bath, and a 2nd full shared bath upstairs. Fourth bedroom on main floor can be used as office/flex space.Beautiful renovated eat in kitchen with stainless steel appliances, new quartz countertops, sink, disposal, faucets, windows, and tile backsplash.Clean indoor air quality provided by high efficiency furnace built with whole house humidifier and carbon clean Merv 16 filter. New sliding doors open to the extensively landscaped fully fenced backyard, a new Mexican Beach pebble accented patio, 3 foot rock wall. New front patio surrounded by blooming white Iceberg roses.New front and backyard sprinkler system. SELLER IS OFFERING BELOW MARKET FINANCING!!!
